{"type":"text","timestamp":1775882717074,"sessionID":"ses_28524b697ffeTsmQ13eGzrEk2C","part":{"id":"prt_d7adbb55c0015LYEMSyzS8MnGv","messageID":"msg_d7adb71d7001Q5lsysMJvSpEsR","sessionID":"ses_28524b697ffeTsmQ13eGzrEk2C","type":"text","text":"## AR-031 RBAC Configuration Summary\n\n### Completed ✅\n\n**Core Implementation:**\n- ServiceAccount templates for all three components (controller-manager, workload-manager, router)\n- RBAC templates (Role + RoleBinding) for controller-manager and router  \n- ClusterRole + ClusterRoleBinding for workload-manager\n- Helper templates for ServiceAccount name generation\n- Complete values.yaml configuration structure\n\n**Testing:**\n- 24 comprehensive unit test cases covering all RBAC resources\n- 5 integration test scripts for permission verification\n- 3 security test scripts (least privilege, no wildcards, token automount)\n- Complete test documentation\n\n**Documentation:**\n- Implementation summary document\n- RBAC architecture and permissions matrix\n- Configuration options and examples\n- Security features documentation\n\n**Security:**\n- Principle of least privilege implemented (router: secrets only, controller-manager: no default permissions)\n- No wildcard permissions (all explicit verbs)\n- Dedicated ServiceAccounts per component\n- Namespace isolation (except workload-manager cluster-wide access)\n\n**All Acceptance Criteria Met:**\n- All templates follow naming conventions\n- Permissions correctly configured per component\n- Role bindings correctly reference ServiceAccounts\n- Values configuration supports enable/disable and customization\n- Comprehensive test coverage\n\n### Deferred 📋\n\n**Future Enhancements** (out of original scope):\n1. Pod Security Policy support\n2. NetworkPolicy RBAC for inter-component communication\n3. Dynamic RBAC rule updates\n4. Audit logging annotations\n5. Multi-tenant namespace-specific RBAC overrides\n6. Automated RBAC testing in CI/CD\n7. ServiceAccount token rotation policies\n8. External RBAC integration (OIDC-based authentication)\n\n**Status:** Production-ready with all original requirements completed. Future enhancements planned for subsequent iterations.","time":{"start":1775882717072,"end":1775882717072}}}
